{"tid":2357041,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"萬科The Campton加推第5張價單　折實平均呎價19,511元","createTime":"2021-01-07T07:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T17:08:35.000Z","uid":44783,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f792a291457f3f3802b638172ddb70cff2a921a1","tid":2357041,"uid":44783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:30:57.000Z","msg":"萬科香港長沙灣住宅項目The Campton，推出第5張價單，涉及47伙，有10伙開放式單位、9伙1房單位、24伙2房單位及4伙3房單位，實用面積介乎272至761平方呎，市值逾4億元。價單定價由612.2萬至1622.2萬元，計及最多16%折扣，折實價介乎514.3萬至1362.7萬元，折實呎價17737至21119元。 萬科香港市場營銷與客戶關係部副總裁劉淑貞說，今日開價之後就會開始收票，計劃在月中開售，這批單位有高層及有海景，定價都是以此調整，認為對客戶有吸引力。 她指出，雖然疫情對於客戶可能有心理影響，但本港經濟仍然正面，看好今年市況。她說，掃管笏項目「上源」都正在以現樓形式，推售洋房及特色單位，西邊街項目亦會招標發售單位，至於何文田全新項目就會在年中考慮推出。"},{"pid":"983c8833c224257e73879aabb696f8b40dd1137f","tid":2357041,"uid":321157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:38:50.000Z","msg":"想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6de2fdd6970baa3672010af01c67ae28b98e459","tid":2357041,"uid":341649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:44:10.000Z","msg":"又加左幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19f81fc6bf68702189bb28c1a34ba80c508f715","tid":2357041,"uid":44783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6de2fdd6970baa3672010af01c67ae28b98e459","tid":2357041,"uid":341649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:44:10.000Z","msg":"又加左幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:50:42.000Z","msg":"第一張價單7球幾有兩房<br />\n呢張價單得一間兩房係1000萬樓下"},{"pid":"d2b628de58ef0fb24f746cd